-- Blue Financial Services to Post Full-Year Loss of as Much as $140 Million
-- Vernon Wessels
-- 2010-06-15T07:25:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-15/blue-financial-services-to-post-full-year-loss-of-as-much-as-140-million.html

          
          
             Blue Financial Services Ltd., a
South African provider of unsecured loans, said it will report a
loss of between 1 billion rand and 1.05 billion rand in the
fiscal year through February from a profit the year earlier.  
          
          


  


        